feature_content: Give your living room a touch of effortless industrialism with the Workman table. Made of sturdy steel, this table makes a strong statement.
feature_content2: The Workman table is made with top grade steel, which is both stain and water resistant.
feature_content3: Its stainless, sturdy structure makes the Workman a table that is sure to last through decades of stylish living.
feature_content4: The Workman table's ergonomic design ensures that it would fit comfortably into any area. The wheeled feet provide smooth portability, so you can move the table away to accommodate more room.
name: Workman Coffee Table
quote: The Workman collection is casually cool and stylish. Love the wheels!

feature_content: By day, it appears as a design-savvy couch. By night, the Tempo Sleeper becomes the perfect solution to a space-saving stayover with a quick flip of the back rest.  Classy, comfortable and convenient, expect many more overnight visitors with this couch.
feature_content2: The Tempo Sleeper is upholstered with a fabric weave of ultimate comfort and quality, woven  as well as you'll weave your dreams upon this couch.
feature_content3: The Tempo Sleeper is crafted with a sturdy frame of kiln-dried hardwood, giving you the support you need whether sitting or sleeping.
feature_content4: Its pliant foam filling and fixed cushioning provides the comfort and support you'll enjoy as you rest.
name: Tempo Sleeper, Gray
quote: The Tempo Sleeper makes a stylish way of sleeping! While folded up, it  looks like a well-designed couch, but it's comfortable and spacious as a sleeper!

feature_content: Timeless with a twist, the Promenade Coffee Table looks homely and inviting at the top, and manages to surprise with an unconventional leg design. Wood and steel collaborate to create a coffee table that's both classic and modern, fit for any room, any style.
feature_content2: The Promenade Coffee table is made with top grade, durable hard wood, adding a touch of class and quality to your living room.
feature_content3: With a sustainable structure and strong steel legs; this is a classic coffee table that will last for ages.
feature_content4: The table is crafted with smooth, rounded edges, providing a pleasant aesthetic, and comfortable assimilation at the same time.
name: Promenade Coffee Table
quote: This is truly a coffee table fit for any style. The wooden surface gives a homely charm, while the steel legs keep it contemporary.

feature_content: When it comes to versatility and easy style, nothing beats a classic bean bag. A few bold-colored bean bags can give any room a playful, inviting feel.
feature_content2: The bean bag is made from hardy, fine quality canvas, which ensures both comfort and durability.
feature_content3: Light-weight and long-lasting, the bean bag is easy to wash and created to last through many lugs across the room.
feature_content4: With a polystyrene bead filling, the bean bag is sturdy, yet flexible, gently conforming to the contours of your body any which way you sit.
name: Bean Bag, Gray
quote: The bean bag is a great addition to any contemporary household! Rest assured that this is one furniture piece you can drag around without worry. Love the bright colors too!
